These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
2 different pets are kept: fish, turtle
1. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer |
| Pet   | turtle     | fish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, lizard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, folk
1. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | lizard   | goat      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | folk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, rock
City: liverpool, boston
1. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | r&b    |
| City     | liverpool | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, zombie
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | zombie |
| Hobby   | photography | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, ship
1. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Flower   | marigold | begonia |
| Transport     | ship    | bus    |

