.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, august
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, bus
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
2. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Birthday   | august | may |
| Transport     | bus   | bike    |

